PZ Deep Research was independently implemented as a consumer-facing deep
research web application. Its early design references ideas from:

  Alibaba-NLP/DeepResearch
  https://github.com/Alibaba-NLP/DeepResearch
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Referenced ideas include deep-research agent workflows, search/visit tool
roles, and XML-style tool-call protocols. This repository does not distribute
the upstream Qwen model weights, datasets, evaluation assets, or the upstream
reference repository.

